<paragraph id="DC7636E27C4BFFF3858825F3FC8BFD3D" blockId="19.[189,1399,511,649]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">The material has been poorly preserved, thus the shells are considerably softened, and the tissues are rather contracted. No attempt has been made to examine the hinge, as the valves are so soft that they do not survive being separated. However, the distinctive external form of the shell and the anatomy are sufficient to describe it and place it at the family level.</paragraph>
